Pre-Pull Data for Recipes with Data Sync

Use data sync to pull data to CRM Analytics on a regular schedule. By scheduling sync from Salesforce and remote systems ahead of time, your recipes have less to do and run faster.

Use Data Sync with Recipes

Recipes can use data previously synced to CRM Analytics or unsynced, direct data.

Use Data Sync with Dataflows

Data sync makes your dataflow runs faster by extracting all data upfront and syncing it to CRM Analytics.
